/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e645a32e9c7e9b21833c81964615c390fe92d64","tid":2274030,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港樓市愈來愈「唔對路」，但不少樓市KOL仍然視而不見，繼續唱好樓價。理由不外乎三個因素，分別是「剛需」、「高收入人士買樓」及「銀紙貶值」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nON <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓價繼續上升, 係因為發展商出呼吸PLAN, D人可以無視風險高價買入, 價錢不斷創新高<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔怕用呼吸PLAN, 因為3年後上唔到會, 仲有林鄭定息PLAN 比佢地轉"},{"pid":"7f0c88f0817576e2e7f3281c1dc46c981d7e7da4","tid":2274030,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"老貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee27d56d228208c545297d18073fa7f254fc3137","tid":2274030,"uid":264771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"買買買 快d買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c6f3e80ce941e8ae13634f2a7e385fb00321e5","tid":2274030,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa9f54edbdd44e8d11c892abf551bfef4df3037","tid":2274030,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"同大陸啲招數一樣 抬高二手樓價 等d人轉買一手樓cap水 實際二手樓你要打折先賣得出"}]}